Create a reporting group.

Creates a reporting group. Make sure the reporting group's name is unique within an account. > Note: Due to the complexity of the request body for this function, where possible, it's recommended that you retrieve an existing reporting group, edit it locally, and pipe the object to this command.
Request body, either as a PSCustomObject or string. This parameter supports pipelining.
